{"tid":625850,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"睇戲唔需要睇影評","createTime":"2018-04-11T19:20:24.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-12T01:19:00.000Z","uid":5375,"like":8,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"b621ff082ecb9535e347878c4aa5181069543dfd","tid":625850,"uid":5375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T19:20:24.000Z","msg":"有無人從來唔睇？尤其係標榜解讀<br />\n當然詮釋同一啲拍攝資訊無妨，<br />\n<br />\n小說、遊戲同樣，上網睇影評等同抹殺自我，當然你可以參與一個類似讀書會形式既討論，前提係首先要有自己既想法<br />\n<br />\n記得十年前學校要做剪報，我通常上高登集思廣義抄內容，但大個啲就知道no way<br />\n<br />\n諸位認同否？"},{"pid":"0123d85537c9260c98e538a78e9096332fa50817","tid":625850,"uid":5375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T22:57:57.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"a844108d28e2f4ba8882e60323b66e5ef757397e","tid":625850,"uid":22898,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T23:05:16.000Z","msg":"其實依加好多所謂「影評」都係垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n成日只係識得講個故仔有咩深度，有咩內涵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我承認有電影係值得去分析去解讀，但係唔係套套電影都係講故仔呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n電影最重要既鏡頭藝術、後製依啲根本無咩人睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n之前黑豹拍得咁垃都比人吹奏就知，黑豹就係「有故仔，冇技術」既例子，成套戲拍到成舊屎咁"},{"pid":"86529146212f3b087760a56d4b4dc0d54cbee083","tid":625850,"uid":22898,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"a844108d28e2f4ba8882e60323b66e5ef757397e","tid":625850,"uid":22898,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T23:05:16.000Z","msg":"其實依加好多所謂「影評」都係垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n成日只係識得講個故仔有咩深度，有咩內涵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我承認有電影係值得去分析去解讀，但係唔係套套電影都係講故仔呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n電影最重要既鏡頭藝術、後製依啲根本無咩人睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n之前黑豹拍得咁垃都比人吹奏就知，黑豹就係「有故仔，冇技術」既例子，成套戲拍到成舊屎咁"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T23:06:56.000Z","msg":"其實有時睇影評，係學佢個賞析，睇下一套戲有咩做麥好，有咩做得唔好<br />\n<br />\n要睇就睇講電影藝術既影評，我自己打影評好少講故仔，都係講電影藝術"},{"pid":"ec488f6c24c99307686437d9e283a118fb5c227b","tid":625850,"uid":42283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T23:06:58.000Z","msg":"睇下HK Movie果D一兩句好短真性情果D就得"},{"pid":"a69bfce8e33ba405118b66f433ac9c596a2599f8","tid":625850,"uid":55851,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"ec488f6c24c99307686437d9e283a118fb5c227b","tid":625850,"uid":42283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T23:06:58.000Z","msg":"睇下HK Movie果D一兩句好短真性情果D就得"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T01:19:00.000Z","msg":"打手嚟架喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}